headline: Textron Contract Win And Record Revenue Raise Questions On Durability
summary: Textron (NYSE:TXT) secured a $163.4 million contract to supply Mobile Strike Force Vehicles to Ukraine. The company reported record annual revenue alongside momentum in its Aviation and Bell segments. Bell's MV-75 program moved production ahead of schedule, signaling operational progress across the defense portfolio.
